I'll tell you another one that gave me pause. A friend of mine years ago
hooked up a pair of internal scoops, aluminum dryer hose, and a bug vent fan
and tried forcing more cooling air to the fan shroud. He could actually see
the head and oil temp drop on his dash when he cranked up the speed on the
fan. A little too busy in the engine compartment for me!

